article_title: Rep. Katrina Shankland: Here's a to-do list for Wisconsin lawmakers
article_text:
Madison, WI (53711)

Today

Partly to mostly cloudy skies with scattered thunderstorms during the morning. High around 85F. Winds SSW at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Variable clouds with scattered thunderstorms. Low 63F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 40%.

article_metadata.description: Taking federal money for BadgerCare and investing in our infrastructure are among the ways to get Wisconsin working for everyone.
article_metadata.author: KATRINA SHANKLAND | Democratic member of Assembly from Stevens Point
